" ambiente ``XINFERENCE_MODEL_SRC=modelscope`` para alterar a fonte do modelo"
" para ModelScope, o que resulta em downloads mais rápidos na China "
"continental."

#: ../../source/getting_started/troubleshooting.rst:88
msgid ""
"If you’re starting Xinference with Docker, include ``-e "
"XINFERENCE_MODEL_SRC=modelscope`` during the docker run command."
